name: Mobil Ijo
description:
Hasil olah digital foto mainan anak saya, dia menyebutnya "mobil ijo". Setiap hari dipakai main dari pagi hari hingga menjelang tidur pun dia letakkan disebelah bantalnya. Mainan yg sangat dia suka ini sekarang sedang rusak, doakan kami selalu diberi rejeki dan kesehatan karena sementara kami berperan menggantikan mobil ijo untuknya. 

digital processing photos of my child's toys, he calls it "mobil ijo".  Every day he used to play from morning until he went to bed, he put it next to his pillow.  The toy that he really likes is currently broken, please pray for us to always be given good fortune and health because in the meantime we play a role in replacing the green car for him.
